slides.title: Map of the Uber controversy in UK
slides.text:
At the map 6 English news media are represtened in relation to the Uber controversy. We have searched their databases for articles using the word Uber, Uber taxi, Uber driver for example.
- The Guardian
- BBC
- The Week
- Telegraph
- Independent
- The Sun
Choosing these news media we believe that each of them will contribute to a nuanced picture of the controversy through different angles and viewpoints.
